      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Ninjutsu (Fuuton)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 4</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 6</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 17 | <b>Successes:</b> 2</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 5 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 17</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> C, S</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>You fire a drilling blade of air that deals 4d6+4 wind damage to the target, and continues onward to affect all other creatures in the target's square and the square behind it (relative to you), dealing half damage to all other creatures hit.</p>\n\n\n\n",
